reviews.review_text: Nice as usual. Many tourists who barely speaks English slow down line to turtle speed. The best option is to order through the phone Mac app with pick up at this location. Fast and efficient service. Young ladies working behind the counters were courteous and polite even though they were running a very busy location. Fries were fresh and milk shakes were good too. Its well located along with other famous fast food restaurants in the same food court. Most of other restaurants were closed on Sunday after 7pm except a very few.
